                     <interp inst="t18390513-1661-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390513-cd-168" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390513-1661-offence-1 t18390513-cd-168"></join>4th of February</rs>, 1 cloak, value 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18390513-name-1099" type="victimName">
