                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I had never parted with the cloak, only for him to take to Mr. Gale Jones—he was to bring me the money or the cloak—he had it three times, and pawned it all three times.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I have bought left-off things repeatedly of him, and he had this to sell, as he wanted to buy cloth for a great coat—it was to be 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.—I was to get what I could over for myself—I intended to pay him when I saw him.</p>
